      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoBase",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoBase.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for asynchronous demonstrations using Task and CancellationToken.\nIdeal for complex asynchronous logic, awaiting multiple operations, or integrating with Task-based APIs.\nThis class inherits from <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoBase\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to provide metadata and logging functionality.</p>\n"
    },
