        }
      },
      "version": "",
      "Uid": null,
      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for demonstrations using Unity Coroutines (IEnumerator).\nSuitable for tasks that are tightly integrated with the Unity lifecycle or for users\nwho prefer the standard StartCoroutine pattern.\nInherits from <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoBase\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> to provide metadata and logging functionality.</p>\n"
    },
