      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.CustomColorTag.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">A ScriptableObject that defines a custom color mapping for text tags.\nUsed to associate a specific string tag with a color for rich text processing within the DemoKit log system.</p>\n"
