      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoBase.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Base class for all demonstration components.\nProvides common functionality for metadata management, logging, and lifecycle hooks.\nThis class is inherited by <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.AsyncDemoBase\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and <xref href=\"Chobitech.DemoKit.CoroutineDemoBase\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.</p>\n"
