      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Chobitech.DemoKit.DemoOrchestrator.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">The central controller for the DemoKit system.\nIt manages the lifecycle of demonstrations, coordinates between UI components (Header, Footer, Log, Description),\nand handles asynchronous execution and cancellation of demo processes.</p>\n"
